OL,3,CLabour win Avon and Somerset PCC for
OL,4,Cfirst time
OL,6,FThe Labour Party have won the police
OL,7,Fand crime commissioner election for
OL,8,FAvon and Somerset, taking the post
OL,9,Ffrom the Conservatives.
OL,11,FClare Moody, the region's Labour
OL,12,Fcandidate, beat her Conservative
OL,13,Fpredecessor Mark Shelford by more than
OL,14,F4,000 votes.
OL,16,FThe win means she has become the first
OL,17,FLabour candidate to be elected into
OL,18,Fthe role since it was created.
