OL,4,Cfirst time
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "I know I am the first Labour
OL,8,Fcandidate to be elected for this area
OL,9,Fand that's a privilege, and I also
OL,10,Frecognise that it's a responsibility."
OL,12,FMs Moody, who was an MEP for South
OL,13,FWest England between 2014 and 2019,
OL,14,Fsaid tackling knife crime will be one
OL,15,Fof her biggest priorities in her new
OL,16,Frole but will "take time."
