OL,6,F"It is a huge issue and it has an
OL,7,Fimpact beyond the consequences of the
OL,8,Fterrible actions we've seen," she
OL,9,Fsaid. "It's a complex problem and
OL,10,Frequires a complex response."
OL,12,FShe added: "A lot of it is about
OL,13,Fprevention work. It's about working
OL,14,Fwith young people in schools and
OL,15,Freinforcing youth services, as well as
OL,16,Fproviding alternative routes so we
OL,17,Favoid the situation in the first
OL,18,Fplace."
