OL,6,FMs Moody said she also hopes to make
OL,7,Fpolicing more visible within
OL,8,Fcommunities.
OL,10,F"By building neighbourhood policing,
OL,11,Fyou're building trust in the police,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"Those connections will help to
OL,15,Fprevent problems and will be about
OL,16,Fcreating a positive policing agenda -
OL,17,Fthat the police are the community and
OL,18,Fthe community are the police," added
OL,19,FMs Moody.
