OL,6,FLast elected in 2021, police and crime
OL,7,Fcommissioners oversee policing within
OL,8,Ftheir police force area, aiming to
OL,9,F"cut crime" and "deliver an effective
OL,10,Fand efficient service."
OL,12,FThey are chosen by the public to hold
OL,13,Fthe Chief Constable to account and to
OL,14,Fensure the force is answerable to the
OL,15,Fcommunities they serve.
