OL,4,Cfirst time
OL,6,FChief Constable Sarah Crew ` who
OL,7,Fattended the election count ` said:
OL,8,F"Democracy has made its mark tonight.
OL,9,FI'm really looking forward to working
OL,10,Fwith the new police and crime
OL,11,Fcommissioner designate to help her
OL,12,Fbuild her police and crime plan to
OL,13,Fhelp her build on her priorities that
OL,14,Fhave led to her being successful
OL,15,Ftonight.
OL,17,F"But I am also really grateful for the
OL,18,Fwork that the outgoing police and
OL,19,Fcrime commissioner has done with me,
OL,20,Fwith tackling the issues in Avon and
OL,21,FSomerset," she added.
